<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Line" xml:lang="en"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v2"/><ttm:agent type="group" xml:id="v1000"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" leadingSilence="0.460"><translations/><songwriters><songwriter>Konnie Aoki</songwriter><songwriter>Sakiel Kiriya</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata></metadata></head><body dur="3:46.519"><div begin="5.068" end="9.732" itunes:songPart="Intro"><p begin="5.068" end="9.732" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1">描いていく My World</p></div><div begin="19.773" end="30.972" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="19.773" end="23.170" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1">いつだって憧れは衝動</p><p begin="23.230" end="25.392" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1">走り出す鼓動のHeat</p><p begin="25.402" end="28.529" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1">飛んでった一際の閃光</p><p begin="28.539" end="30.972" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1">追いかけてStarting now</p></div><div begin="31.070" end="41.654" itunes:songPart="Verse" ttm:agent="v2"><p begin="31.070" end="32.927" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v2">I don't care! So, I don't care!</p><p begin="32.937" end="36.126" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v2">関係ないな Watch me! 罵詈雑言</p><p begin="36.464" end="38.296" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v2">Right away, so, right away</p><p begin="38.320" end="39.131" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v2">止まんないな</p><p begin="39.141" end="41.654" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v2">Step to what my soul dreamt</p></div><div begin="41.664" end="56.522" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="41.664" end="44.112" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1">無限大の夢を</p><p begin="44.422" end="46.727" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2">Never-ending hope</p><p begin="46.737" end="49.401" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1">輝いた瞬間を</p><p begin="49.411" end="52.279" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2">Extending fate unfolds</p><p begin="52.289" end="56.522" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1000">I am ready to start!!</p></div><div begin="56.665" end="1:19.690" itunes:songPart="Chorus" ttm:agent="v1000"><p begin="56.665" end="57.623" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1000">Let's move on!</p><p begin="57.626" end="59.691" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1000">Right now, Right now!</p><p begin="1:00.251" end="1:03.639" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1000">弾けた世界 遊び廻れ</p><p begin="1:04.106" end="1:06.955" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1000">時は満ち足りた Show time</p><p begin="1:07.393" end="1:08.311" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1000">Go for it!</p><p begin="1:08.321" end="1:10.333" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1000">I know, I know</p><p begin="1:10.990" end="1:15.129" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1000">抱えた願い 熱狂の先へ</p><p begin="1:16.267" end="1:19.690" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1000">形振り構わず Super Duper YEAH!</p></div><div begin="1:29.799" end="1:40.245" itunes:songPart="Verse" ttm:agent="v2"><p begin="1:29.799" end="1:32.122" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v2">This tale's unfolding on its own</p><p begin="1:31.574" end="1:32.650" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v2">So, Liven up!!</p><p begin="1:32.660" end="1:34.258" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v2">No bumps in my way 騒げ</p><p begin="1:34.268" end="1:35.131" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v2">Yeah! Stand up!!</p><p begin="1:35.141" end="1:37.814" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v2">Unexpected chance has come up</p><p begin="1:38.126" end="1:40.245" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v2">Get ready to seize it on</p></div><div begin="1:40.393" end="1:51.008" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="1:40.393" end="1:45.387" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1">期待以上 そのVision 1000%のポジティブで Ride on!</p><p begin="1:45.626" end="1:51.008" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1">今きっと 光を狙い撃ち DASH!! 個性の解放</p></div><div begin="1:51.018" end="2:05.991" itunes:songPart="Verse"><p begin="1:51.018" end="1:53.660" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v2">Braveness in the soul</p><p begin="1:53.670" end="1:56.111" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1">可能性をLock on</p><p begin="1:56.121" end="1:59.390" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v2">Advancing towards my goal</p><p begin="1:58.722" end="2:01.284" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1">揺らいでたまるか根性</p><p begin="2:01.710" end="2:05.991" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1000">最高速で突破!!</p></div><div begin="2:06.047" end="2:28.925" itunes:songPart="Chorus" ttm:agent="v1000"><p begin="2:06.047" end="2:06.964" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1000">Let's move on!!</p><p begin="2:06.974" end="2:09.122" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1000">Right now, Right now!</p><p begin="2:09.605" end="2:12.962" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1000">選べる未来 走り廻れ</p><p begin="2:13.442" end="2:15.838" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1000">花盛りキミ次第だ</p><p begin="2:16.626" end="2:17.547" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1000">Go for it!</p><p begin="2:17.599" end="2:19.548" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1000">I know, I know</p><p begin="2:20.269" end="2:24.419" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1000">派手に飛び交う限界の先へ</p><p begin="2:25.554" end="2:28.925" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1000">新時代を駆け巡れ So, Dive in!</p></div><div begin="2:49.670" end="2:59.068" itunes:songPart="Verse" ttm:agent="v1000"><p begin="2:49.670" end="2:52.037" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1">終わりのない希望を</p><p begin="2:52.414" end="2:54.733" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v2">Unstained emotions</p><p begin="2:55.108" end="2:59.068" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1000">煌めいた Dream up</p></div><div begin="2:59.382" end="3:22.445" itunes:songPart="Chorus" ttm:agent="v1000"><p begin="2:59.382" end="3:00.226" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1000">Let's move on!</p><p begin="3:00.275" end="3:02.238" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1000">Right now, Right now!</p><p begin="3:02.962" end="3:06.193" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1000">弾けた世界 遊び廻れ</p><p begin="3:06.753" end="3:09.449" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1000">時は満ち足りた Show time</p><p begin="3:10.009" end="3:10.866" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1000">Go for it!</p><p begin="3:10.914" end="3:13.097" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1000">I know, I know</p><p begin="3:13.586" end="3:17.938" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1000">抱えた願い 熱狂の先へ</p><p begin="3:18.854" end="3:22.445" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1000">形振り構わず Super Duper YEAH!</p></div></body></tt>